name: Collect me
description:
I heard a distant voice.
I felt named
although I never had a name.

I searched through the grass,
following the sweet sound.

In a field of daisies
I found it.
One daisy among thousands,
almost the same as all the others.
But she was singing:

"Collect me, please.
I don't want to keep my feet on the ground anymore.
The world is wounded
and I feel its pain taking root in me.
Collect me".
